item.description:
@Javacisnotrecognized wrote:

You can’t have more than one server running at a time, or be playing RS and MoparScape at the same time, or use the webclient and run a server at the same time, or be using that port, etc, etc.

Solution: dissconnect your internet service, and then reconnect it and that will go away.
